{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351670/extras/1.gif?t=1736006351\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Power of Elemental Combinations: Create New Magic</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine elements and attribute magic freely on scrolls to create entirely new spells! With over 30 unique and vibrant combinations to discover, the possibilities are endless. Whether you craft a blazing fire spell or conjure a magical garden of blooming flowers, unleash your creativity to shape magic beyond imagination. Experience the power of creation as you weave spells onto the scrolls!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351670/extras/2.gif?t=1736006351\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Blank Scrolls, Ready for Your Magic</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Start with an empty scroll and create magic your way. Fill the blank scrolls with your unique style\u2014whether elegantly intricate or brilliantly efficient. The choice is yours to make every spell truly one of a kind!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351670/extras/3.gif?t=1736006351\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Stories of Diverse Customers</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From scrolls for magical education to those destined for ancient ruins, a wide variety of customers will visit your shop with unique requests! Understand their needs and craft the perfect magic scrolls to fulfill their demands. Complete orders successfully to earn tokens and repay your debt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And who knows? You might even encounter customers with far more secretive and mysterious needs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351670/extras/4_1.gif?t=1736006351\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Special Customers</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Not all customers are ordinary! Meet a cast of colorful characters: a young adventurer embarking on her first journey, a bard seeking to immortalize forgotten legends through song, an explorer delving into ancient ruins, and a jovial yet fearless dwarf with a heart of gold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Their requests may be challenging, but the rewards\u2014and the hidden stories they reveal\u2014are worth the effort. Support their adventures with your magical creations and uncover the secrets they carry!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Junior Scrollmaker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3351670/1157a0fa48ef8e31b5f37753f324236bca4a19c0.jpg"},{"name":"Nope, invalid!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3351670/befcc0b0f5172c6004e13564a30e3e3c7c6aea4a.jpg"},{"name":"Veteran Scrollmaker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3351670/fb800a70380b9285f8f6c770035ecfd58dbaf1fd.jpg"},{"name":"Mater Scrollmaker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3351670/308b1e775fad7117a03b54d0954afb154d579dd3.jpg"},{"name":"Top-notch Service","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3351670/86d29f380b2f86bec2933a73cee92544e8c06244.jpg"},{"name":"Freedom!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3351670/db6042c0788c72ba15c99a5f06968c1fce136c4d.jpg"},{"name":"Diligent Payer","path":"https://cdn.akama