 ruins, and a jovial yet fearless dwarf with a heart of gold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Their requests may be challenging, but the rewards\u2014and the hidden stories they reveal\u2014are worth the effort. Support their adventures with your magical creations and uncover the secrets they carry!</p>","developers":["InTheBox"],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351670/header.jpg?t=1736006351","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257081388,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257081388/movie480.mp4?t=1734321779","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257081388/movie_max.mp4?t=1734321779"},"name":"Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257081388/b76ea3b6e088a593e03e43b1f3436d060ba2eeec/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1734321779","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257081388/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1734321779","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257081388/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1734321779"}}],"name":"ENSCROLL","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel i3-6100 / AMD FX-8350<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 8 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> GeForce GTX 1050Ti<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> Version 12<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 2 GB available space</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel i7-6700<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 16 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> Geforce RTX 9